Class AbstractDiscreteFeature<P,​DO>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.rdg.resc.edal.feature.AbstractDiscreteFeature<P,​DO>
  • Type Parameters:
    P - The type of object used to identify positions within the feature's domain. This may be a spatial, temporal, or combined spatiotemporal position.
    DO - The type of domain object
